                              ኃጢአት።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#115va">115va</locus>: This is a Missal of (the church
                              of) John the Baptist, which is Dabra Betel Kʷäkʷälo … John the
                              Baptist. He who steals it or erases (its text) shall be
                              excommunicated. Its scribe is Gabra Giyorgis. So that it might be for
                              him the salvation of his body and soul … (and) the absolution of
                              sins.</quote>
                           <note> </note>
                        </item>
